reviewText: "Photography Sensual Video" is a collection of short video sequences of photographic ideas that both amateur and professional will find beneficial. The producers obviously spent time and attention on each video sequence in order to explore a sensual idea. Each video snippet explores a completely different scenario and each sequence is different from one another. Not Hollywood production values, but it doesn't detract from the idea being explored. Although there is nudity, it is not pornographic in any manner. Exceptional model selection and it's always educational to see how a photographer interacts with their subjects to achieve the desired effect. A worthy photographic exploration.
